This is a Service Agreement between TechVentures India Pvt Ltd and Ramkumar Palanivel.
Effective Date: April 14, 2026. Payment Terms: INR 75,000 per month.
The consultant shall deliver AI platform architecture, including Rambot Enterprise modules.
Key obligations: Complete the DocuMind RAG pipeline by June 2026.
The developer must submit weekly progress reports every Monday.
Risk: Late delivery penalty of 10 percent per week after deadline.
The agreement shall be governed by Indian contract law.
Both parties must sign the NDA before project commencement.
Payment shall be made within 15 days of invoice submission.
